name: charming leaf pendant
description:
This polished gold plated leaf pendant is strung from a dramatically long 25" gold plated round cable chain, adorned with a mint opal glass stone pendant, and secured with a gold plated lobster clasp.

Fun, flirty and fabulous.

name: long leaf filigree earrings
description:
“Every leaf speaks bliss to me, fluttering from the autumn tree” ~ Emily Bronte

Dangling from french ear wire are delicate gold plated filigree leaf pendants. They measure about 3" in total length.

Casually elegant.

name: flirty feather earrings in brown leopard
description:
A pair of brown genuine leopard feathers hang gracefully from silver ear wire. Feathers are approximately 3" and earrings measure about 4" total length.

Fun. Flirty. Fabulous.

name: double chain filigree leaf necklace in silver
description:
Truly a spectacular piece. Dare I say my favorite?

A silver leaf filigree dangles 3" from one of two dramatically thick, round silver plated cable chains. Chains measure 26" and 29" in total length. Secured with a lobster clasp.

The perfect gift for someone who likes to look spectacularly simple. Or a really good excuse to buy something new for yourself.

Background art from my personal collection and courtesy of the very talented Hadley Hutton... http://hadleyhutton.etsy.com

name: dramatic rose ring in ivory
description:
"A rose is a rose is a rose." ~ Gertrude Stein

Adjustable, wide band silver plated ring is adorned with a fantastically dramatic 1.5" ivory resin rose.

Make a statement without making a fuss.
